item.dc:creator: @Haxor_X Haxor X
item.description:
@Haxor_X wrote:

i don’t know how to make this simpler except to go to your house and change for you…

its very simple…

when it says illegal start of expression
add a } above it…

ex.
illegal start of expression
public int blah blah
^

change to this

}
public int blah blah

then when it says ‘)’ expected
add a ‘)’ where it says…

ex.
‘)’ expected
blah blah int(98989898 ,blah blah
^

change to
blah blah int(98989898) ,blah blah

ok got it???
